## Production Notes

- Change the default `admin@wgportal.local` / password before exposing to the internet
- Restrict port `8888` to known IPs in the security group — it's your VPN management UI
- Port `51820/udp` can stay open to `0.0.0.0/0` — that's the WireGuard tunnel and needs to be reachable by VPN clients
- Consider putting wg-portal behind a reverse proxy with HTTPS for production
- `registration_enabled: true` lets any Keycloak user in the realm register — set to `false` and manage users manually if you want tighter control